&lt;li&gt;Identify friction points and adoption gaps through usage data, customer interviews, and feedback loops with Customer Success and Sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and prioritize a backlog of targeted product enhancements that drive measurable improvement in customer stickiness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support roadmap planning alongside senior PMs, contributing well-reasoned prioritization recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
