&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain dashboards and reports that track adoption trends across customer segments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate quantitative findings into clear product hypotheses and actionable backlog items&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Data Science and Engineering on instrumentation improvements and event tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
