&lt;li&gt;Work co-op with product managers and other stakeholders to learn more about FourKites products and services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in the Agile software development life cycle to draft, revise, and validate a series of product/technical documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help educate internal and external FourKites users with the latest changes in the product by working closely with our product and go-to-market experts as they evangelize the new releases within our application&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on strategic projects related to documentation and the FourKites Community&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
