&lt;li&gt;Translate ambiguous customer requirements into structured, engineering-ready backlog items with clear scope boundaries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own sprint-level backlog grooming in collaboration with the engineering manager, ensuring tickets are well-defined and prioritized before each cycle.&lt;/li&gt;
